summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department and to the award for Parcel 52 in connection with the condemnation for the widening of Southwest Roxbury Street (King County Cause No. 743336, Ordinance 99805), providing for reimbursement to the Arterial City Street Fund from which payment of certain condemnation awards and costs were made pursuant to Ordinance 101604, from the Urban Arterial Trust Account from funds to be received from King County and by appropriation from the Arterial Development Fund.
